      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PENNY PINCHER (2) stalked the lead and fought on well to finish one length away in third (22.85) at this track in a Grade 6 over 400m. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card last start despite being beaten. Can measure up this time. SUNSET VENDETTA (1) doesn't have the best strike-rate but recent form is sound. Finished in the minors last time when second (22.81) at this track making it back to back placings. Didn't win last time but still ran one of the quickest times on the card. Expected to be in the finish again. TYCOON ZULU (3) finished third (23.44) two back at this track but out of the placings last time when 7th there. Should be about the mark. MERL'S LAD (8) has ability and finds the right scenario to bounce back.",
